            <h3>What Researchers Want</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Edit proposals in their IDE (VS Code, Cursor)</li>
              <li>Use AI assistants (Claude Code, Copilot)</li>
              <li>Version control with Git</li>
              <li>Automated compliance checking</li>
              <li>Collaborate without email chains</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="gap-card gap-exists">
            <h3>What Exists</h3>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Research.gov:</strong> Web-only, no API, manual validation</li>
