              <li><strong>Proposal Central:</strong> Web forms, no AI integration</li>
              <li><strong>Google Docs:</strong> Better collaboration, zero validation</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="gap-conclusion">
          <strong>The gap:</strong> No tool treats grant proposals as structured data that
          AI can read, validate, and help write. That's what we're building.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

